data.description: Space inside and out! The convenience of a single-story home is yours to enjoy in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch-style home, which is situated in Merkel TX, on 2.67 acres, with relaxing rural views in every direction. Inside is an open floor plan that includes vaulted ceilings, a wood burning fireplace and neutral tones that will compliment any decorative style. The updated kitchen has quartz counters and custom cabinetry. The primary bedroom is ensuite and includes a walk in closet. The other two bedrooms are connected by the Jack and Jill restroom which is equipped with individual toilets and sinks on both sides. Finally, 2 spaces of the 3-car garage have been converted into a large bonus room which would be a wonderful game room or additional bedroom.  Outside, the rock wall surrounds the back yard including a large shop with electricity.  Make this space yours today!
